org.libav.avformat.bridge

Class AVInputFormat54

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bridj.NativeObject
      • org.bridj.StructObject
        • org.libav.avformat.bridge.AVInputFormat54
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NativeObjectInterface

    public class AVInputFormat54
extends StructObject
    Mirror of the native AVInputFormat struct from the libavformat v54.x.x. This class contains only the public API fields, the real AVInputFormat struct is bigger. For details see the Libav documentation.
    Author:
    Ondrej Perutka
